                        "content": "A client with leukemia is receiving busulfan and allopurinol. The nurse would plan to tell the client that the purpose of the allopurinol is to prevent which problem?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nAllopurinol decreases uric acid production and reduces uric acid concentrations in serum and urine. In the client receiving chemotherapy, uric acid levels increase as a result of the massive cell destruction that occurs because of the chemotherapy. This medication prevents or treats hyperuricemia caused by chemotherapy. Allopurinol is not used to prevent alopecia, nausea, or vomiting.",
                        "id": "29f05ab5b29a4718b30467ee05569db3",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "6b6b0d2a361b449e815634b39f51cb00",
                                "content": "Platelet count"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "4be7bde01a584f5fbaefa4837719ee26",
                                "content": "Bone marrow biopsy"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "6e3901aae4624186ae6f17f5294d7717",
                                "content": "White blood cell count"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "ab42a0c2640c46859977d4f57540012a",
                                "content": "Complete blood cell count"
                            }
                        ],
